summary:
I have done 3 months of internship in marketing at Brand24 and finished several marketing CXL courses. I am fully motivated to learn more and get to know all the marketing insights.

Now I am a junior marketing assistant at Brand24.

My experience may not be vast, but when you hire me, you'll be surprised how fast I learn : )

Don't believe me? I speak 3 foreign languages fluently and am learning the 4th one.
